snippet.title: SPACESONA - Original Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Download my original game SPACESONA for free!  https://kazehita.itch.io/spacesona
Journey to the edge of the universe to escape the end, find meaning of life, and find friends! Or, maybe die.

SPACESONA is a short visual-novel type adventure game, about making good choices in the moment, and about having good luck! 

Music by https://x.com/damahysk/

Stay tuned by following me on social media https://kazehita.carrd.co/
